        public java.lang.String getMask()
        Description copied from interface: IgnoredFileDescriptor
        Ignored mask represent ignore pattern in ignore files for different VCS (e.g. .gitignore, .hgignore, etc). The recommend way to support all VCS is to choose common pattern for mask. Note: At the moment this mask will be written to ignore file without any pre-processing (as it is)
